Class SpaceObject

java.lang.Object
SpaceObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Administrator, Debris, Policymaker, Satellite, Scientist, SpaceAgencyRepresentative, TrackObjectsInLEO, UnknownTypeObject
public abstract class SpaceObject extends Object
This class is designed to model an object in space, whether it be debris or a satellite.
